# ── STEP 2: Creator stores use a FIXED path + query param ────
#
# uyehtech.com/marketplace/creator-store?store=uyeh-store&product=ID&ref=CODE
#        → serves /marketplace/creator-store.html
#        → store, product, ref are read client-side from the query string
#
# No dynamic :storeSlug catch-all — store identity lives entirely in
# ?store=, not the path. This is intentional: it avoids ever silently
# 404-masking a mistyped /marketplace/whatever as if it were a real store.

